task.action:
Create `src/types/event-ledger.ts` with the following exports:

- `EventLedgerParams` interface: { tagIds: string[], startDate?: string, endDate?: string, accountId?: string, skip?: number, take?: number }
- `EventLedgerTransaction` interface: { id: string, name: string, amount: number, type: "expense" | "income", date: string, categoryName: string, subcategoryName?: string, accountName: string, tags: { id: string, name: string, color: string }[] }
- `EventLedgerResponse` interface: { totalExpenses: number, totalIncome: number, netAmount: number, expenseCount: number, incomeCount: number, transactions: EventLedgerTransaction[], hasMore: boolean }
- `EventLedgerTagParams` interface: { transactionId: string, transactionType: "expense" | "income", tagId: string }
